            "subtype": "range",
            "text": "15 feet",
            "type": "stat_block_section",
            "unit": "feet"
          },
          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "The veldenar raises the viscosity of the surrounding air just by breathing it. Creatures who enter or start their turn within the emanation treat the area as difficult terrain and take a \u20132 status penalty to any non-magical physical attacks they attempt. This aura is suppressed whenever the veldenar has a creature engulfed.",
